Why it’s distinct from “meaning”

Meaning asks:
	•	what does this point to?

Myth / religion asks:
	•	what story can carry this through generations?
	•	what symbolic frame makes this actionable and memorable?
	•	what ritual stabilizes it?

So:

meaning = interpretation
myth = durable symbolic architecture
religion = myth + ritual + authority + continuity


